# Permuter runs: stdout-streamed log files under permute_log/<func>.log
# (brief 063). The `perm_work/` directory is the wrapper's staging
# area (already ignored implicitly since nothing has ever checked it
# in). The auto-runner creates `permute_log/` when invoked with
# `--run`; keep those out of the repo.
permute_log/
perm_work/

